COMPUTERS are MACHINES That EXECUTE ALGORITHM

- Fixed programs computer
  
  - fixed set of algorithm
  - What we had until 1940's

- Store program computer

  - Machine stores and execute instructions 

- Key insight: Programs are no different from other kind of data
=====================================================================
STORED PROGRAM COMPUTER
=====================================================================

- Sequence of instruction stored inside computer

  - Built from predefined set of primitve instructions

1) Arithmetic and logical
2) Simple tests
3) Moving data

- Special program(interpreter) executes each instrucion in order

  - Use tests to change flow of control through sequence
  - Stops when it runs out of instructions or executes a halt instruction
