BASIC PRIMITIVES
=====================================================================

- Turing showed that you can compute anything with a very simple machine with only 6 primitevs: left, right, print, scan, erase, no op

- Real programming languages have
  
  - More convenient set of PRIMITIVES
  - Ways to combine primitives to create new primitives

- Anything computable in one language is computable in any other programming language
